Package: budgie-weather-applet
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: budgie-desktop weather applet
 A budgie-desktop applet for displaying the weather in the panel.
 With the choice of two providers controlled through the applet
 settings, this applet displays the weather in an easy to
 view manner
